    <h2 id = "pros">The Pros of Being a Teacher</h2>
    
    <li id = "good"> It is totally worth it! Just seeing a child develop is exciting to watch, and knowing you're the reason behind it will make you feel great! </li> <br>
    
    <li id = "good">It is enjoyable! Interacting with children can be fun and entertaining. Students love to find ways to make their teachers smile and laugh. Just having a good time improves their ability to learn and you'll still be doing your job.</li>
    
